<p>According to <a href="https://foundationinc.co/lab/generative-engine-optimization">research from Foundation Inc.</a>, 63% of companies that have optimized for GEO report increased visibility. And 86% of enterprise SEO teams have already integrated some form of AI optimization into their workflow.</p>
